{"tid":143900,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"如何回到當時😭","createTime":"2017-03-05T04:19:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-05T12:29:24.000Z","uid":83863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c19b84dfa147f29f6d0940599a14551e68c6650f","tid":143900,"uid":83863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T04:19:16.000Z","msg":"同男友一齊咗年半，大家番工時間唔夾，近幾個月開始少咗傾計。<br />\n我需要搵人傾訴時佢仲訓緊，所以會轉而同朋友傾訴，因為佢地即時俾到feedback我。<br />\n佢就不嬲都好少講自己嘢，但早幾個月發現佢原來同上一份工嘅女同事有傾心事，發現之前我連有呢個人都唔知，因為佢一直都唔會講呢啲嘢。佢話需要一個人傾訴拍拖時遇到嘅問題，已經特登搵一個有拍拖嘅人嚟傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n發現完之後，即使佢咁講，其實我到宜家都成日因呢個人而唔開心，因為成日覺得佢哋單獨傾得好密，而我又知道個女仔係我男友有興趣果type<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 出街有時望到男朋友whatsapp頭幾個會係佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我心入面好唔鍾意，最近次次見都會係喊住走咁，好心淡，心淡在自己咁小家，因為講真佢哋乜都無做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同男友講，男友就講話只係朋友，需要搵人傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n利申：男友之前好多情史 而佢係我第二個男朋友 所以我無乜安全感"},{"pid":"74cfea4fda687662310723fcf809a5aec068b4c2","tid":143900,"uid":21202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T04:45:24.000Z","msg":"似佢移情別戀"},{"pid":"ed8c6a27cbd458d7164ee08dbbd37cfe155e656d","tid":143900,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T04:49:06.000Z","msg":"男人不壞 女人不愛"},{"pid":"0934babba4f64c7e662b5e491094c88201850c42","tid":143900,"uid":83863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T08:14:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26edb9d93fbc59403436587d8187c3694a23a486","tid":143900,"uid":33040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T09:27:28.000Z","msg":"如何回到熱戀的那時"},{"pid":"d20eb2d72c3216579e6bf5f749fb1eace1363526","tid":143900,"uid":72342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T09:30:34.000Z","msg":"情侶最易分手係 出黎做野時間唔岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81b61c2da7869f50b8717f6f35b4870c9f936ad1","tid":143900,"uid":83863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T11:43:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>情侶最易分手係 出黎做野時間唔岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同埋大家睇嘅世界開始有分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74c9f9af3998749fa61472d028ab378536a5ddc4","tid":143900,"uid":86541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T12:29:24.000Z","msg":"感情變淡左<br />\n試下同佢講自己感受，拍拖遇到咩問題就拎出黎講<br />\n話自己好唔開心<br />\n<br />\n如果佢唔理你感受既話，咁呢種男朋友要黎都冇用"}]}